{"tid":601983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國鋼鐵鋁稅豁免名單再擴大　歐盟、阿根廷、澳洲、巴西、南韓等國可豁免","createTime":"2018-03-22T16:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T02:43:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8d42cf7ef31d13c39c2840a460726480cbddb1f0","tid":601983,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"美鋼鐵鋁稅豁免名單再擴大　歐盟、南韓等國可豁免<br />\n<br />\n2018/03/22 23:11<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普的懲罰性鋼鋁關稅將於美國時間周五上路，法新社剛剛報導，美國暫時豁免對南韓課徵鋼鋁關稅。路透報導指稱，美國貿易代表萊特海澤透露，這一波豁免名單還包括歐盟、阿根廷、澳洲、巴西。<br />\n<br />\n稍早，美國貿易代表萊特海澤（Robert Lighthizer）出席眾議院賦稅委員會聽證會時透露，將與南韓在現有貿易談判中，討論可能豁免安排。<br />\n<br />\n川普將對鋼鋁分別課徵25%與10%關稅，但已承諾豁免加拿大與墨西哥。<br />\n（張翠蘭／綜合外電報導） <br />\n&lt;台灣蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"1eade3b06a341bfa380518dd66b170fed41ef2ae","tid":601983,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180322/1320366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180322%2F1320366&d=9r6hOT1uquhmcijAzKx0j54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d204bf91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180322%2F1320366&h=c286a4dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180322/1320366</a>"},{"pid":"c8bdd56518bcb7871f8128620d3a7bcae4291585","tid":601983,"uid":38904,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"美國向全球收稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大部份國家都有豁免<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只有中國冇份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass